  <p>The QR codes, which can be presented to regular customers by printing on the magnet, can also be sent to homes with brochures, if desired. Many companies that want to provide package order service with <strong>QR menu</strong> have started to prefer this application. In addition to the cost of printing the menu, it is also possible to design the menus in desired shapes. The ugliness of the design and the fact that it is unalterable are thus eliminated.</p>
  <p><h3>In-Business Order</h3></p>
  <p>Customers who want to order from homes will make it easier to enter orders via internet connection and QR code application. They will not encounter any surprises as they will order by seeing the amount they will pay. In addition, within the company:</p>
  <ul>
  <li>Fixed QR codes can be placed on tables,</li>
  <li>Customers can access the menu with these codes,</li>
  <li>They can forward their orders without contacting the waiter.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>This application, which will become widespread and used much more frequently during and after the pandemic, provides unlimited service to its customers and makes it easier to apply the desired menu type.</p>
  <p><h3>Fast and Reliable System</h3></p>
  <p>You will be able to update the price through the application. The system, which provides businesses with the cost of printing the menu again, allows you to both save paper and show that you care about the health of your customers. The application, which is produced in accordance with all mobile phones, allows phones to access the menu quickly.</p>
  <p>This system, which will support your corporate image, is known for enabling contactless shopping. The application, which enables menus to be opened on the screen of the phones in seconds, is realized with a simple camera setting.</p>',

